@startuml DFD_Level0_Context
!theme plain
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

title Award Monitoring & Tracking System - Data Flow Diagram (Level 0 - Context)

' External Entities (Sources/Sinks)
rectangle "Employee" as employee #LightBlue
rectangle "Faculty Secretary" as fac_sec #LightGreen
rectangle "Dean" as dean #LightYellow
rectangle "Rector's Office" as rector #LightCoral
rectangle "System Admin" as admin #LightGray

rectangle "University LDAP" as ldap #Pink
rectangle "AI Service" as ai #Pink
rectangle "Email Server" as email #Pink
rectangle "SMS Gateway" as sms #Pink
rectangle "File Storage" as storage #Pink

' Main Process (System)
agent "Award Monitoring\n& Tracking\nSystem" as system #White

' Data Flows - Employees
employee --> system : Award Data,\nDocuments,\nProfile Updates
system --> employee : Award Status,\nNotifications,\nPublic Awards

' Data Flows - Faculty Secretary
fac_sec --> system : Review Decisions,\nApprovals/Rejections
system --> fac_sec : Review Queue,\nFaculty Reports

' Data Flows - Dean
dean --> system : Role Assignments,\nApproval Decisions
system --> dean : Faculty Analytics,\nEscalated Reviews

' Data Flows - Rector's Office
rector --> system : Final Approvals,\nPolicy Decisions
system --> rector : University Dashboard,\nExecutive Reports

' Data Flows - Admin
admin --> system : System Config,\nUser Management
system --> admin : System Logs,\nHealth Metrics

' Data Flows - External Systems
system --> ldap : Auth Requests
ldap --> system : User Credentials,\nEmployee Data

system --> ai : Documents for Parsing
ai --> system : Parsed Metadata,\nConfidence Scores

system --> email : Notification Messages
system --> sms : Alert Messages

system --> storage : Document Files
storage --> system : Stored File URLs

' Notes
note right of system
    **Core Data Processing:**
    • Award CRUD operations
    • Multi-level workflow
    • Document AI processing
    • Analytics & reporting
    • GDPR compliance
end note

@enduml



